summary: Killing Eve is my new crack ...  - soooo good!  Sandra Oh is amazing in it and so was Jodie Comer!  I can't believe she didn't...
question: Killing Eve is my new crack ...  - soooo good!  Sandra Oh is amazing in it and so was Jodie Comer!  I can't believe she didn't get nominated, really question the reasoning behind that one.  I haven't seen the Americans so I have no idea about Keri Russell, but Sandra Oh definitely deserved that nomination and the win, should be interesting to see how that goes on GG night.
answer: Right??? Jodie Comer got robbed!!! Such an amazing show. We need more gender bending shows. Too bad Sense 8 got cancelled. I binged in a day so if anyone is looking for a show to watch, Killing Eve is it. I’m so-and-so about The American but Keri Russell is a powerhouse and her performance has been consistent throughout the seasons. She’s overdue for a win but I really want Sandra Oh to walk away with the GG!
